data.description: Check out this charming open concept split foyer home located in the heart of downtown Hiram. Huge level lot and not in a subdivision! As you enter the freshly painted interior home, you are greeted by a spacious well-lit living room with a cozy gas log fireplace. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, breakfast area, pantry, and laundry closet. The dining room is conveniently located adjacent to the kitchen, making it easy to serve and enjoy meals. The Owner Suite has a double trey ceiling and provides plenty of space for rest and relaxation, along with the well-lit bathroom featuring a massive soaking tub, separate shower and double vanity. The secondary bedrooms are inviting and comfortable while the attic is spacious and perfect for extra storage. The basement offers endless possibilities for additional bedrooms, media room, gym or spa. You can make this area whatever you want. The oversized garage and outbuilding with power are perfect for all the tools and lawn equipment. Additionally, the property boasts a lovely backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and enjoying the Georgia weather. Whether you want to have a barbecue, create a garden oasis, or simply relax and soak up the sunshine, this back yard and oversized deck aim to please. In terms of location this property is conveniently located to nearby shopping centers, restaurants, parks, schools, and the hospital. Making everyday errands and activities easily accessible. This one is a must see!!
